Interface ReadFile<T>

  • Type Parameters:
    T -
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ReadCombo, ReadWigleWifi

    public interface ReadFile<T>
    This interface defines three methods : readFile, readBuffer, and inputObject. Then, two classes implements this interface : @see ReadWigleWifi, @see ReadCombo.

    The main goal of this interface his to read a file. We are able to read a Wigle Wifi file, or a combo file.

    Author:
    Orel and Samuel.
